data.name: rtbOutput.Text
data.value: Step 1: Choose the serial port for your UART device, and press connect UART. Step 2: Once UART is connected, set Idle (Tx Low). Step 3: Plug in battery. Step 3: Once battery has been plugged in set Active (Tx High). Step 4: Set Idle (Tx Low) before unplugging battery and/or disconnecting the serial port. ===========================================================
